<!-- Template: 中国风格-变体25 (Content #1635) - 君子四德·居中图+四品格环绕 -->
<div class="w-[1440px] h-[810px] relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #FAF9F6;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex">
        <!-- 左侧区域 -->
        <div class="w-[560px] flex flex-col px-16 py-12">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <h1 class="text-[40px] font-serif mb-3" style="color: #1F1A14;">君子四德</h1>
                <div class="w-14 h-[2px] mb-4" style="background-color: #7A1B1B;"></div>
                <p class="text-[22px] font-serif" style="color: #7A1B1B;">梅兰竹菊</p>
                <p class="text-[14px] mt-2" style="color: #7A6B5D;">傲雪凌霜，幽香清雅，虚心有节，淡泊高洁</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 单图 -->
            <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/placeholder.svg" alt="梅兰竹菊" style="width: 400px; height: 400px;" class="object-cover" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 右侧四品格 -->
        <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-2 grid-rows-2">
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-10" style="background-color: #F0EBE1;">
                <p class="text-[32px] font-serif mb-3" style="color: #7A1B1B;">梅</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-[1px] mb-3" style="background-color: #C4A882;"></div>
                <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.8]" style="color: #4A3728;">不畏严寒，坚韧不拔。凌寒独自开，暗香浮动。</p>
                <p class="text-[12px] mt-3 italic" style="color: #B8A99A;">"遥知不是雪，为有暗香来"</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-10" style="background-color: #1F1A14;">
                <p class="text-[32px] font-serif mb-3" style="color: #C4A882;">兰</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-[1px] mb-3" style="background-color: #4A3728;"></div>
                <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.8]" style="color: #B8A99A;">空谷幽香，清雅脱俗。不以无人而不芳。</p>
                <p class="text-[12px] mt-3 italic" style="color: #4A3728;">"芝兰生于深林，不以无人而不芳"</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-10" style="background-color: #1F1A14;">
                <p class="text-[32px] font-serif mb-3" style="color: #C4A882;">竹</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-[1px] mb-3" style="background-color: #4A3728;"></div>
                <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.8]" style="color: #B8A99A;">虚心劲节，高风亮节。咬定青山不放松。</p>
                <p class="text-[12px] mt-3 italic" style="color: #4A3728;">"宁可食无肉，不可居无竹"</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-10" style="background-color: #F0EBE1;">
                <p class="text-[32px] font-serif mb-3" style="color: #7A1B1B;">菊</p>
                <div class="w-8 h-[1px] mb-3" style="background-color: #C4A882;"></div>
                <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.8]" style="color: #4A3728;">凌霜自芳，淡泊名利。花中隐士，不争春色。</p>
                <p class="text-[12px] mt-3 italic" style="color: #B8A99A;">"采菊东篱下，悠然见南山"</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 底注 -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
        <p class="text-[12px]" style="color: #B8A99A;">中国画题材 · 文人画四君子</p>
    </div>
</div>